{"id": "1440759517326344383", "channel_id": "1440759517326344383", "type": 0, "author_id": "126439705934954497", "author_name": "sephallia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I first noticed this when trying to complete story mode achievements that say \"Deal atleast X dmg in a single turn in elite/final battle.\"\n\nI run Castor in my team so I make use of the plume corrosion. I do all my set up, the enemy has enough HP for me to get the achievement if I successfully burst it that turn. I do my turn and burst it, but upon finishing the map the achievement was marked as \"Not Achieved.\"\n\nI think I've also noticed in general that \"turn damage\" number displayed in battle on the top right does not match with the actual damage that I do when corrosion is involved. I did not actually record video or screenshots of this phenomenon, but I can make sure to do so a little later if necessary.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T17:43:56.948000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440759517326344383", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "CORROSION and TOTAL DAMAGE not reflecting properly.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
